forever grateful 4 these beauties 4 trusting me & allowing me 2 grace their face w/ my heartwork 💖

if money wasn’t a thing, i’d do this for free. i love what i do and i’m thankful that i’m able to get paid to do what i love. i always tell people that the business side & pricing is the hardest part of my job because this comes easy to me but its everything that comes with it that makes it “work”. i truly appreciate my clients for not trying to bargain my prices and respect my art because they understand that this is also my job. Being able to build connections while expressing myself through this craft is priceless.
